#  Chapter 2: Lines
When drawing a line, each segment (an unbroken straight line part) should get progressively bigger or smaller.

even lines:= Each segment or [[cluster___20240619_095817|cluster]] is of the same length.

There are gaps in even lines which may need anti-aliasing

